\[h_{\theta,P}(y)=\log\int_{t\leq 0}\exp\Bigl{(}-\|P_{S}^{\frac{1}{2}}(t-\theta _{S})+(P_{S})^{-1/2}P_{SS^{c}}(y_{S^{c}}-\theta_{S^{c}})\|^{2}/2\Bigr{)},\]

