\[h_{\theta,P}(y) =\log\Bigg{(}I_{2}+\int_{t\leq 0,t\in\Omega_{1}}\exp\Bigl{(}-\|P_{S }^{\frac{1}{2}}(t-\mu)\|^{2}/2\Bigr{)}\Bigg{)},\] \[\text{where }I_{2} \leq(2\pi)^{\frac{|S|}{2}}\Big{|}P_{S}^{-\frac{1}{2}}\Big{|}e^{- r^{2}}.\]

